caller_intent: Jennifer Brock wants to transfer insurance coverage from a 2013 Chevrolet van to a new 2014 Chevy Express van for her husband's company, as part of purchasing a new vehicle.
resolution_steps: Agent Jeff verified the policy details (four vehicles, including the 2013 van).
Obtained the VIN for the new 2014 Chevy Express van.
Confirmed coverage details (comp deductible of $1,000, no collision, towing up to $100).
Clarified the vehicle is for business use only and has no lien.
Agreed to send a proof of insurance email to Jennifer Brock at jenniferbrock1000@gmail.com.
summary: Jennifer Brock requested a vehicle insurance transfer from a 2013 Chevrolet van to a new 2014 Chevy Express van. The agent verified policy details, confirmed coverage parameters, and agreed to send a proof of insurance email. The transfer was completed during the call.
